block layout-content
  br
  // Hero Section
  section.bg-gradient-primary.py-5
    .container
      .row.align-items-center
        .col-lg-10.mx-auto.text-center
          h1.display-4.fw-bold.mb-3
            i.bi.bi-gear-wide-connected.me-3
            | Modernizing Client Libraries in .NET Framework Applications
          h2.h3.mb-4 From LibMan to Modern Build Systems: A Complete Transformation Guide
          p.lead.mb-5
            | Transform your legacy .NET Framework 4.8 application with modern client-side tooling. Learn how to migrate from outdated LibMan dependencies to a cutting-edge npm/Webpack build system, achieving 52% faster load times and 63% smaller bundle sizes while maintaining backward compatibility.

  // Main Article Content
  article#main-article
    .container
      .row
        .col-lg-8.mx-auto

          // Executive Summary
          .card.mb-5.border-success
            .card-header.bg-success.text-white
              h3.card-title.mb-0.fw-bold
                i.bi.bi-check-circle.me-2
                | Executive Summary
            .card-body
              p.lead The evolution of web development has brought powerful new tools that can significantly enhance legacy applications. This article documents the complete modernization of client-side libraries in a .NET Framework 4.8 application.

              .row.g-3.mt-2
                .col-md-6
                  .card.border-primary.h-100
                    .card-body.text-center
                      i.bi.bi-speedometer2.display-6.text-primary.mb-2
                      h6.card-title.fw-bold 52% Faster
                      p.card-text.small Page load time improvement

                .col-md-6
                  .card.border-success.h-100
                    .card-body.text-center
                      i.bi.bi-file-zip.display-6.text-success.mb-2
                      h6.card-title.fw-bold 63% Smaller
                      p.card-text.small Bundle size reduction

              h5.mt-3.fw-bold Key Achievements:
              ul.list-group.list-group-flush
                li.list-group-item
                  i.bi.bi-check-circle-fill.text-success.me-2
                  | Migrated from LibMan to npm for dependency management
                li.list-group-item
                  i.bi.bi-check-circle-fill.text-success.me-2
                  | Implemented Webpack-based build system with asset bundling
                li.list-group-item
                  i.bi.bi-check-circle-fill.text-success.me-2
                  | Upgraded to Bootstrap 5.3.8 from Bootstrap 4.x
                li.list-group-item
                  i.bi.bi-check-circle-fill.text-success.me-2
                  | Enhanced DataTables from v1.x to v2.3.3 with advanced extensions
                li.list-group-item
                  i.bi.bi-check-circle-fill.text-success.me-2
                  | Added modern JavaScript libraries (D3.js, C3.js, Slick Carousel)

              .card.mt-4.border-info
                .card-body.text-center
                  h6.card-title.fw-bold.mb-3
                    i.bi.bi-globe.me-2
                    | Experience the Modernized Application
                  p.mb-3 See the performance improvements and modern UI enhancements in action with the fully modernized Data Analysis Demo application.
                  a.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg(href='https://dataanalysisdemo.markhazleton.com/', target='_blank', rel='noopener')
                    i.bi.bi-box-arrow-up-right.me-2
                    | Visit the Updated Site
                  p.small.text-muted.mt-2 Experience 52% faster load times and modern responsive design

